column5: Hey everyone,i know we are all booked in as well as gerritt,right on ...how bout wayne??? i think roy was going to talk to him,is he going or should someone get in touch with him,im sure he will want to go....cheers   shawn

Roy says he is already booked since last November.He will be in our neck of the woods next week so Roy will talk to him.Rumor has it Wayne will have to dock his boat at the cement plant with the canada steamship or he will have to pay for 2 boat slips custom made at Merlands.We will have to shuttle him out to his boat

I'm sure he'll be there I don't think he misses a chance at quinte...and I owe apologies to carp "remo" sorry buddy! You were good enough to invite me to your boat and I once again am truly sorry. No excuse I guess power or no power...
